            "list": [
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "desc": "<p>This sword has an extraordinary full name:<br>The Triumphant Harbinger of Dawn that Points Towards Victory.<br>Only one has ever fallen by this blade on the battlefield.<br>One night, the bearer drew the sword triumphantly.<br>The night sky lit up as bright as day,<br>pin-pointing his precise location.<br>Arrows rained down upon him.</p>",
